Package: secubox-mac-guard
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), nftables, nginx, ieee-data
Recommends: nmap, arp-scan
Description: SecuBox MAC Guard - MAC Address Control
 MAC-based network access control with device discovery, vendor lookup,
 whitelist/blacklist management, and nftables integration.
 .
 Features:
  - MAC address whitelist/blacklist management
  - Device discovery and tracking via ARP/DHCP
  - OUI vendor lookup (ieee-data)
  - Device naming and tagging
  - Alert on unknown devices
  - nftables MAC filtering integration
  - Real-time device monitoring
 .
 Port Debian bookworm SecuBox module (CyberMind.fr).
